{"featured_counts":0,"common_counts":21,"collapsed_counts":0,"reviewing_counts":0,"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/answers/560964320/root_comments?include=data%5B%2A%5D.author%2Ccollapsed%2Creply_to_author%2Cdisliked%2Ccontent%2Cvoting%2Cvote_count%2Cis_parent_author%2Cis_author\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=4\u0026order=normal\u0026status=open","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/answers/560964320/root_comments?include=data%5B%2A%5D.author%2Ccollapsed%2Creply_to_author%2Cdisliked%2Ccontent%2Cvoting%2Cvote_count%2Cis_parent_author%2Cis_author\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=2\u0026order=normal\u0026status=open","totals":6},"data":[{"id":566450651,"type":"comment","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/comments/566450651","content":"呃(~_~;)至于为什么那么多人会开喷估计是出于什么心理，我想回答一下。\u003cbr\u003e我一只大二狗，学过初等数论这门课，早就对哥猜有一定了解，在课程学习中就对哥德巴赫猜想产生敬仰之心。\u003cbr\u003e我刚刚看到这个问题的时候是有些生气的，首先是这个问题的提法很怪，“如果我证明了哥猜能进清北吗”，给人一种“证明哥猜是为了进北大”的感觉，这是一种对知识本身的不尊重，“进清北”的含金量根本没法跟证明哥猜相比，这也是对哥猜身为“数学皇冠的明珠”这一赞誉的贬低。\u003cbr\u003e其次是一种功利思想，退一万步讲，或许题主真的证明了哥猜的一部分，但是这种以学术成果换取入学资格的想法是真的非常不可取。","featured":false,"collapsed":false,"is_author":false,"is_delete":false,"created_time":1545905986,"resource_type":"answer","reviewing":false,"allow_like":true,"allow_delete":false,"allow_reply":true,"allow_vote":true,"can_recommend":false,"can_collapse":false,"author":{"role":"normal","member":{"id":"f78a0d17005e77eb4196aaee83e56586","url_token":"darkkiva","name":"Darkkiva","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-37c1e5852b075b38b36cac322968778e_r.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-37c1e5852b075b38b36cac322968778e_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/f78a0d17005e77eb4196aaee83e56586","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false}},"vote_count":4,"voting":false,"disliked":false,"censor_status":0,"child_comment_count":4,"child_comments":[{"id":566455800,"type":"comment","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/comments/566455800","cont